line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">1</span><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: black;">、</span><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 153);">用车</span><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: black;">：<span style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">正规空调旅游车，根据实际人</span>数安排车型，保证一人一个正座；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: 微软雅黑, tahoma, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;"><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: black;">2</span><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 153);">、门票：</span><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: red;">薰衣草庄园</span><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: black;">；（备注：由于门票已按旅行社优惠价核算，所以老年证、学生证等证件不退还门票款，自愿放弃游览景区景点不退还门票款）；　　　</span></span></p><p style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: 微软雅黑, tahoma, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;"><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: black;">3、</span><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 153);">住宿</span><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: black;">：2-3人标准间，（如产生单男单女，我社有权调整为三人间，如住单间，需另补房差。（酒店名字参考住宿说明）</span></span></p><p style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: 微软雅黑, tahoma, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;"><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: black;">4、</span><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 153);">膳食</span><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: black;">：</span></span><span style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: black;">含餐2早4正餐（10人一桌8菜1汤、四荤四素；人数不足十人菜品，相应减少；（花湖中餐自理；高原地区条件限制，餐饮质量较差，，望做好心理准备、团餐因是桌餐或套餐，不用餐都无费用可退；尽请谅解；（草原、九寨沟沿线住宿提倡绿色环保，酒店都不提供一次性洗漱用品，请游客自备，景区酒店定时供应热水））</span></p><p style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: 微软雅黑, tahoma, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;"><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: black;">5、</span><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 153);">导游</span><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: black;">：持证导游服务</span></span></p><p style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: 微软雅黑, tahoma, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;"><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: black;">6</span><span style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 153);">、保险</span><span style