; color: black;">2-3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: black;">人标准间，（如产生单男单女，我社有权调整为三人间，如住单间，需另补房差。（酒店名字参考住宿说明）</span></span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 1.75em"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: black;">4</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: black;">、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 153);">膳食</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: black;">：</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: black;">含餐2早4正餐（10人一桌8菜1汤、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: black;">四荤四素；</span>人数不足十人菜品，相应减少；（花湖中餐自理；高原地区条件限制，餐饮质量较差，，望做好心理准备、团餐因是桌餐或套餐，不用餐都无费用可退；尽请谅解；<span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: black;">（草原、九寨沟沿线住宿提倡绿色环保，酒店都不提供一次性洗漱用品，请游客自备，</span>景区酒店定时供应热水<span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: black;">）</span>）</span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.75em; MARGIN: 0px 0px 2px"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: black;">5</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: black;">、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 153);">导游</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: black;">：持证导游服务 </span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.75em; MARGIN: 0px 0px 2px"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: black;">6</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 153);">、保险</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: black;">：含保</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; color: black;">额10万元旅游意外险；</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, 