><br/></p>', N'<p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24px"><strong><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">费用包含</span></strong></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">1</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">、</span><strong><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">【交通】</span></strong><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">：根据实际人数选用豪华空调旅游车，保证一人一个正座（散客接送为出租面包车接，接送不配导游 ）</span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">2</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">、【</span><strong><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">门票</span></strong><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">】：青城山+都江堰（备注：门票优惠按我社与景区协议，优惠退票20元/人，全免退40元/人）</span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">3</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">、【</span><strong><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">用餐</span></strong><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">】：含一次正餐10元/人，标准十人一桌，8菜1汤（备注：自愿放弃用餐，不予退费）</span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">4</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">、【</span><strong><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">导游</span></strong><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">】：全程一位优秀持证中文导游，提供“一站式”导游服务。</span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">5</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">、【</span><strong><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">保险</span></strong><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">】：旅游意外险（最高赔偿额10万，最终解释权归保险公司所有）</span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: " color:="">重要提示：保险名单必须提前一天提供给旅行社，如不主动提供视为自动放弃保险，由带来的一切损失及后果旅行社概不承担任何责任。</span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">2.</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">青城山电瓶车往返20元/人，索道往返60元/人（单程35</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: ">元/人）</span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 